      *  APLICAÇĂO:        ARQUITECTURA                               **
      *  MÓDULO:           PARAMETROS                                 **
      *  FUNÇĂO:           TRATAMENTO DE ERROS RCODE - ETCL0002       **
      *  PROGRAMA:         VIAP0022.                                  **
      *  CRIACAO:          2011.12.28                                 **
      *  AUTOR:            VIA CONSULTING                             **
      *  DESCRIÇĂO:        PROCEDIMENTO PARA TRATAMENTO DE RCODES     **
      ******************************************************************
      *           L O G     D E     A L T E R A C O E S                *
      ******************************************************************
      *  INICIO  * AUTOR  * FIM    *  C O M E N T A R I O S           **
      *          *        *        *                                  **
      ******************************************************************
       VIAP0022-TRATA-RCODE.

           MOVE ETCL0002-RCODE TO VIAW0020-RCODE.

           IF VIAW0020-RCODE-INF
              SET ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS TO TRUE
           END-IF
           IF VIAW0020-SEM-ERROS
              SET ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS TO TRUE
           END-IF.
           IF VIAW0020-RCODE-VAL
              SET ETCL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO TRUE
           END-IF.
           IF VIAW0020-RCODE-APL
              SET ETCL0002-ABEND     TO TRUE
           END-IF.
       VIAP0022-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

